trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpression"></xref> objects.

The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpressionCollection> class provides a simple collection object that can be used to store a set of <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpression> objects.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpressionCollection"></xref> class.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpressionCollection"></xref> class containing the specified array of <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpression"></xref> objects.
An array of <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpression"></xref> objects with which to initialize the collection.
one or more objects in the array are `null`.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpressionCollection"></xref> class containing the elements of the specified source collection.
A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpressionCollection"></xref> with which to initialize the collection.
value is `null`.
Adds the specified <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpression"></xref> to the collection.
The <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpression"></xref> to add.
The index at which the new element was inserted.
Copies the elements of the specified array to the end of the collection.
An array of type <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpression"></xref> containing the objects to add to the collection.
value is `null`.
Adds the contents of another <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpressionCollection"></xref> to the end of the collection.
A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpressionCollection"></xref> containing the objects to add to the collection.
value is `null`.

A <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeParameterDeclarationExpression"></xref> to search for in the collection.
`true` if the collection contains the specified object; otherwise, `false`.
Copies the collection objects to a one-dimensional <xref href="System.Array"></xref> instance beginning at the specified index.
The one-dimensional <xref href="System.Array"></xref> that is the destination of the values copied from the collection.
The index of the array at which to begin inserting.
The destination array is multidimensional.
